{"tid":2059823,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【35+？】工程界黃偉信：反對攬炒","createTime":"2020-06-11T07:48:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T12:32:49.000Z","uid":221035,"like":17,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d2204715e53c9913e23a8bd964cb3c4349c9f338","tid":2059823,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:48:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1074404?fbclid=IwAR32CPkSu9dxH-cx3STp42uCcNmgAYy_k1seSSDDDLTfNcAO8t-U8x_1NwQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1074404%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR32CPkSu9dxH-cx3STp42uCcNmgAYy_k1seSSDDDLTfNcAO8t-U8x_1NwQ&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=638b25a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1074404%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR32CPkSu9dxH-cx3STp42uCcNmgAYy_k1seSSDDDLTfNcAO8t-U8x_1NwQ&h=d454c79a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1074404?fbclid=IwAR32CPkSu9dxH-cx3STp42uCcNmgAYy_k1seSSDDDLTfNcAO8t-U8x_1NwQ</a><br />\n<br />\n講過好多次，唔好迷信35+<br />\n35+黃碧雲就真係死得<br />\n何況中共今次一定會大玩DQ<br />\n總之我寧願揀後生、本土或者素人，有抗爭意志嘅入去好過<br />\n泛民老實講，係議會入面真係有作用嘅，得3個：許勇、慢必、朱迪<br />\n<br />\n（警告！以下內容可能極唔啱聽）<br />\n好多人會問點解唔計埋鄺神，老實講佢係有落場，不過講到議會抗爭佢真係無做過啲乜，最多就係剪條片「死唔斷氣鬧足10分鐘」俾大家過下癮，同許勇、慢必、朱迪冇得比<br />\n<br />\n不過都唔係重點，重點都係想講有攬炒意志有抗爭意志嘅人先值得選入去！"},{"pid":"38bce664f57aea59b50cc53ffddfbf4458a50744","tid":2059823,"uid":221035,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:49:45.000Z","msg":"我完全唔反對初選，只係提醒大家唔好迷信35+"},{"pid":"26b91d5b276da4155b8033b3deb4e548c61aced7","tid":2059823,"uid":221035,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:50:55.000Z","msg":"好在衛生服務界有余慧明選，講到明攬炒，如果唔係全部功能組別都唔肯攬炒，俾你40+都無用"},{"pid":"1a320ec2019bf4b61f68685401fae7fa038e2cc6","tid":2059823,"uid":214192,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:51:30.000Z","msg":"佢唔諗住攬炒就唔好走去選啦<br />\n咁搞法，咪要36+"},{"pid":"b25dd3da369d27ef8c46a7b6de9dcc4d8c27b3fa","tid":2059823,"uid":18001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:52:05.000Z","msg":"37+了"},{"pid":"891a230d823912b3bfe4ec05003fcf67f17bd2e9","tid":2059823,"uid":262389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:53:01.000Z","msg":"當大家仲係度內鬥嘅時候，麻煩你睇下流亡台灣嘅手足點講<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2059034\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2059034</a>"},{"pid":"61aa82800ff07de81af76ebea7a3a301cfd65022","tid":2059823,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:54:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad97b89d4e030ca23d1fb2e5847e0af08e780b4","tid":2059823,"uid":16518,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:58:42.000Z","msg":"呢個係功能組別wo，普通人冇份投ga，你諗下咩人去投票先啦，係註冊工程師，唔係中產都接近中產，全部都上哂岸，一開始就講到明攬炒仲點選"},{"pid":"0c40fed76bbf188bd9aefda249ba39077f29f08d","tid":2059823,"uid":221035,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4ad97b89d4e030ca23d1fb2e5847e0af08e780b4","tid":2059823,"uid":16518,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:58:42.000Z","msg":"呢個係功能組別wo，普通人冇份投ga，你諗下咩人去投票先啦，係註冊工程師，唔係中產都接近中產，全部都上哂岸，一開始就講到明攬炒仲點選"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:59:41.000Z","msg":"咁所以咪話囉，35+其實根本無預功能組別<br />\n啲界別保守到仆街"},{"pid":"f59c7c63d1a021d76705e0b0610821f396acaf28","tid":2059823,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T08:01:08.000Z","msg":"工程界就情有可原<br />\n唔過財議案，冇工程<br />\n佢個界最傷<br />\n你講明否決財政預算案既話不如唔好選<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae614520a70cfce1e5aaa6f8655b2cb951916d74","tid":2059823,"uid":221035,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f59c7c63d1a021d76705e0b0610821f396acaf28","tid":2059823,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T08:01:08.000Z","msg":"工程界